# =========================
# Apple Rules (Optimized v4)
# Scope: Core services, iCloud, App Store, media, CDN and regional sites
# Excludes: Apple Intelligence / Private Relay (see appleIntelligence.list)
# Notes: Domain-only rules; no shared-CDN wildcard or IP-CIDR rules
# =========================

