# =========================
# Design Notes
# =========================
# - Removed broad shared-provider rules such as akadns.net and crashlytics.com
# - Removed historical, typo, defensive-registration and unrelated domains
# - Kept exact third-party CDN endpoints only when Apple-specific
# - Apple Intelligence and iCloud Private Relay remain in appleIntelligence.list
# - IP-CIDR rules are intentionally omitted to avoid forcing unrelated traffic
